data.description: Step into luxury living with this stunning home in the highly desired community of Monticello located on the border of Murrieta and Wildomar. Enjoy the luxury of modern details, over sized lot, no rear neighbors and the option of an ASSUMABLE VA LOAN with a LOW RATE of 4.99% for qualifying VA buyers. Situated on an elevated lot, this home offers breathtaking hilltop views, providing a private retreat from the hustle and bustle. As you enter, you are instantly greeted with 20-foot ceilings, neutral-painted walls and large windows drawing in an abundance of natural light. The heart of this home undoubtedly lies within its open-concept kitchen, complete with an oversized island that's perfect for both meal preparation and joyful family gatherings. Modern upgrades tastefully adorn this culinary haven, effortlessly merging style with functionality. The kitchen seamlessly transitions into the expansive family room, creating a harmonious space where cherished moments can be shared and everlasting memories created. The formal dining is easily accessible through the butler hallway, ensuring seamless entertaining. Enjoy the convenience of 1 bedroom and full bathroom downstairs, perfect for overnight guests or in-laws. The master bedroom is a retreat in itself, adorned with laminate wood flooring, a modern digital ceiling fan, a remodeled custom shower, dual sinks, and a spacious walk-in closet. The upstairs loft provides flexibility for a home workspace, craft area, or game room. Enjoy 22 PAID OFF SOLAR PANELS saving you significantly on electricity bills so bring your Teslas and blast that AC. The allure of this home extends to the outdoors, where a beautifully landscaped and oversized backyard awaits. Complete privacy with no rear neighbors offers the perfect space to enjoy the hot tub all year long. Take in breathtaking views of the sunset while enjoying the serenity of your private oasis. Conveniently located just minutes away from the 15 and 215 freeways, this home offers easy access for commuters and close proximity to shopping, top rated schools and so much more. This is a home you do NOT want to miss!
